      "sourceStatus": "REDACTION_MARKER_CHECK",
      "sourceText": "Mr. [REDACTED], an artist living at [REDACTED], Chicago, Illinois ([REDACTED]) advised SA [REDACTED] on March 11, 1952 that he saw a flying disc at 9:00 AM on March 6, 1952.",
      "reason": "line_not_translation_ready",
